ly an accretion rate of\n$\\approx 3 \\times 10^{-8} M_\\odot {\\rm yr^{-1}}$ and an electron temperature of\n$\\approx 3 \\times 10^{10}$ K at $\\approx 10$ Schwarzschild radii; the latter is\nconsistent with the brightness temperature inferred from VLBI observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Mar 2007 20:35:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Jun 2007 21:54:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Sep 2007 19:14:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
